            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1173898776" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1173898776" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1173898776">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/2674938/">吟游诗人</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar30 rating" title="还行"></span>
                    <span>2017-04-05</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">应该说新五代史是一部比较让人失望的编撰，欧阳修为了体现他的政治观念，牺牲了史料的相近度和准确度，导致对事件的前因后果往往要参照旧五代史和资治通鉴。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
